<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mʿy ạ̉nt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mʿy ạ̉nt yạ ḥbyby kl ḥyn yạ ḥyạty
 fyk ạ̉ḥyạ yạ nṣyby yạ rjạỷy ạlmwạty
 ạ̉nt ḥqy wṭryqy ạ̹dẖ ḥmlt ly dẖnwby
 ạ̉nt ly kẖyr ṣdyq ạ̉nt ly kẖyr ḥbyb yạ ḥbyby
 2- km ạ̉nạ fyk sʿyd qd hdytny ạ̹lyk
 ḥbk rby mjyd gẖbṭty fy rạḥtyk
 lyt trnymy wsẖkry bl wlytny bqlby
 ạ̉jʿln mnk rjạỷy wạ̉htdạỷy kl drby yạ ḥbyby
 3- kẖlny dwmạaⁿ ạ̉rạk mạlkạaⁿ kl zmạmy
 hạnỷạaⁿ fy mltqạk dạỷmạaⁿ ạ̉nt ạ̉mạmy
 wạḥdạaⁿ ạ̉rjwh rby ạ̉n ạ̉rạk bjwạry
 mạlỷạaⁿ ʿqly wqlby kl lyly wnhạry yạ ḥbyby</lyrics>
